# choco

> The Chocolatey package manager.
> Some subcommands such as `install` have their own usage documentation.
> More information: <https://chocolatey.org>.

- Execute a Chocolatey command:

`choco {{command}}`

- Display help:

`choco -?`

- Display help for a specific command:

`choco {{command}} -?`

- Display version:

`choco --version`
